===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
Alternative descendant of {{m|zh|叓|tr=-}}, which is the ancient form of {{m|zh|事|tr=-}}. Furthermore, both characters are related to [[史]], which was born as a variant without the horizontal stroke on top.

The character should represent a hand holding a flag to mean "representative, ambassador"; see [[使]].

